/blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊有講叫佢唔清球波呀<br />\n我叫佢唔好用頭清咋<br />\n<br />\n我又冇話文尼腳波唔肉酸<br />\n係咁將你自己虛構出黎嘅論點加左落我到就當討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔用頭用條撚清？<br />\n做龍依個情況緊係快手清走個波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上面咪講左囉<br />\n佢係烏低黎頂<br />\n佢跳起用上半身攞波唔得？<br />\n我係講緊咁嘅情況用頭清好危險，個波唔高<br />\n就算人地收腳都會撞埋去個頭到<br />\n做龍係要清個波，但唔理自身安全？<br />\n我冇為文尼個腳波辯護過，佢起腳過高踩到人塊面紅牌係好正常<br />\n你地講到我係咁講文尼腳波冇問題咁做咩？</blockquote><br />\n果個高度用頭好合理wo</blockquote><br />\n唔得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個波彈到頭咁就唔可以頂架<br />\n要慢啲咁跳起用心口<br />\n等文尼攞到波之餘再有機會踩你心口一腳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝刺緊跳起有幾慢？ 側面到會踩心口？</blockquote><br />\n叫龍門心口攞波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d68dab657b09576d1592324c53c80aab8d2f01a","tid":393741,"uid":47585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 道歉托咩 柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擲句埋去<br />\n係呀 係望住個波踢爆你龍門 吹咩<br />\n咁先係架ma</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝口而出嘅意氣說話叫人長抖係唔恰當，雖然係利po講，但的確係唔岩，我只係為我個句意氣言論而道歉，唔明有咩咁柒"},{"pid":"6d4212ab326188f4e2c6e7509c15833ede066a09","tid":393741,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:18:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 道歉托咩 柒撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擲句埋去<br />\n係呀 係望住個波踢爆你龍門 吹咩<br />\n咁先係架ma</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n衝口而出嘅意氣說話叫人長抖係唔恰當，雖然係利po講，但的確係唔岩，我只係為我個句意氣言論而道歉，唔明有咩咁柒</blockquote><br />\n你唔講都講左啦 唔通佢地真係會原諒你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n討論區呢架ja<br />\n道德高地低過現實好多<br />\n如果我講句死獌狗又要道歉<br />\n咁咪好唔得閒"},{"pid":"9662cf83467793164ca2d2093a3a65bcdfac9c4f","tid":393741,"uid":73422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"的確 個龍仲後生係要交下學費 <br />\n慢慢就會學精點樣出迎清到波之餘又保護到自己<br />\n紐亞就係個好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d0c9929a0ec19a5937c936fd49b13cca3650e3","tid":393741,"uid":47585,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個陣時見到文尼紅語氣重左<br />\n<br />\n我原意只係希望呢個龍汲取教訓，面對一個跑咁快嘅球員咁樣用頭解圍真係搵命搏，下下咁樣解圍好易出人命，佢絕對可以有更安全嘅做法去完成解圍<br />\n<br />\n紅牌比左，勝負亦已分<br />\n曼城中場雙閘同一對中鋒完勝利物浦後場，輸得心服口服<br />\n<br />\n如果我嘅言論導致各位不快，係度同各位講返一聲sorry<br />\n<br />\n龍已經康復出院，希望佢繼續有好嘅發揮，上演高水平嘅英超比賽</blockquote><br />\n屌你生滋狗黎架？ 咁無原則既 比人屌兩句就夾住條尾出黎道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都唔明，開口埋口人身攻擊有咩意思<br />\n我衝口而出冇慎言講啲惡毒說話，負責而道歉<br />\n咁就話我冇原則<br />\n出黎串柒柒話係咁茅，咁點？ 又會話我茅西<br />\n反正我點做你都會搵到位話我<br />\n覆完你呢次就廢事再覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5548148a7f12eb2dc50aadc093cf13b1c6a7dca","tid":393741,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2e07de38e90cb39e45321bd21cf1ca44799cfa","tid":393741,"uid":129067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg&h=f486450b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭痢狗豬到傻咗要入阿狗狗竇lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b3d6cdd1fd83cbd6fa5b74e7efd86bf67e21d2","tid":393741,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg&h=f486450b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭痢狗豬到傻咗要入阿狗狗竇lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要係大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bacc3eac758cb9bff4d1c555af7a5a53113e8d4","tid":393741,"uid":71712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:32:13.000Z","msg":"Ederson好撚勇悍，有少少鍾意左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4912321be92ee98b811088d4b0802f90119e0069","tid":393741,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg&h=f486450b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭痢狗豬到傻咗要入阿狗狗竇lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要係大陸仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大陸仔果個好似唔係佢"},{"pid":"5f1aaf918b973757b64290c9b4ae3f1a3e7882c3","tid":393741,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/10/112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F10%2F112020_57faa9caf8bc4bf71221355bd5f8f950.jpg&h=f486450b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n臭痢狗豬到傻咗要入阿狗狗竇lur地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.